track_notes: Track from East side of Bauroux, this track is easy on a good path, can be done in winter time with snowshoes
This track is nice and easy if you are in good health; most is in a forest, so good for summer time, but in winter when snow is there you must have snowshoes. It is about 2 hours to the summit
track_title: Shotest track to Summit from Caille

track_notes: The way down on the east side of the edge is a bit difficult to find and sometimes vertigo!

This is the long way to the Bauroux. The way up is fine and easy on a good path, the way down i used is a bid difficult, but if you follow the yellow marks, it is mich more easy. Get some water in summertime.
Plenty room for par the car, and much room on summit for antenna; nice landscape
From caille walking west to Seranon, you will see the old village and walk into a forest path until the summit. the way down is fine.
